<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Meta Information -->
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0"
    />
    <title>Home Page</title>

    <!-- External CSS -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css"
      type="text/css"
    />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bungee&family=Source+Sans+Pro:ital,wght@0,300;0,600;1,300;1,600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- App CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/layout.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/like__btn.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/nav.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/header.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/stories_new.css" type="text/css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/back-to-top.css" type="text/css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="/styles/responsive-design.css"
      type="text/css"
    />

    <!-- External JS -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <!-- App JS -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/client.js"></script>
    <script
      type="text/javascript"
      src="/scripts/composer-char-counter.js"
    ></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/back-to-top.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/compose.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/nav.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/like__btn.js"></script>

    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
  </head>

  <!-- CDN: timeago -->
  <script
    src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/timeago.js/4.0.2/timeago.min.js"
    integrity="sha512-SVDh1zH5N9ChofSlNAK43lcNS7lWze6DTVx1JCXH1Tmno+0/1jMpdbR8YDgDUfcUrPp1xyE53G42GFrcM0CMVg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous"
    referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
  ></script>

  <body>
    <!-- Top nav bar (fixed) -->
    <%- include('partials/_nav') %>

    <!-- Header (fixed)-->
    <%- include('partials/_header') %>

    <!-- Page-specific (main) content here -->
    <main class="container">
      <!-- COMPLETED STORIES -->

      <h1>My Stories</h1>
      <section class="story-container">
        <a id="title"><b>Story Title</b></a>

        <p class="story-content">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec at
          dapibus est, id faucibus orci. Quisque eget semper odio. Fusce
          porttitor placerat sem, ac semper metus malesuada eu. Mauris massa
          urna, facilisis sit amet ultrices eu, mollis eget diam. Etiam vel nisi
          et leo accumsan cursus. Proin gravida volutpat velit ac commodo.
          Vivamus sed posuere nisi. Sed pellentesque hendrerit mattis. Class
          aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per
          inceptos himenaeos. Pellentesque ornare dictum dapibus. Nullam
          accumsan varius turpis quis ultricies. Quisque sodales tortor ac
          tortor ultrices, quis aliquet erat feugiat. Suspendisse a sem rhoncus,
          eleifend dui a, luctus felis. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora
          torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos.
        </p>
      </section>
      <h1>Create New Story</h1>
      <section class="new-story">
        <section class="error-message"></section>
        <!-- User input story form -->
        <form method="POST" action= "/create/new-story">
        <class class="story-form">
          <textarea
            name="title"
            id="story-title"
            placeholder="Story Title"
          ></textarea>
          <textarea
            name="content"
            id="story-text"
            placeholder="Write your new story here!"
          ></textarea>
          <!-- Submit story -->
        </class>
          <button id="story-button" type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
          <!-- Count characters of collab -->
          <output name="counter" class="counter" for="story-text">500</output>
        </form>
        <!-- Render collab -->
        <section class="story-section"></section>
      </section>
    </main>
    <button class="back-to-top">
      <i class="fas fa-angle-double-up" id="arrow-up"></i>
    </button>
  </body>
</html>
